data.description: **TEMEKU HILLS**   ** PRICE REDUCED 12/1/2023 TO $755,500 **  Upgraded home situated on a quiet cul-de-sac. This home sits on a generous 7,405 sq. ft. !!!40 PANEL PAID SOLAR!!! 4 bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths with loft. Amenities including tile floor, vaulted ceilings and a newly renovated kitchen. Custom quartz countertops, honed marble backsplash, large farmhouse sink and all new stainless-steel appliances. Family room boasts a large fireplace, built in entertainment center, wood plantation shutters throughout the home. The formal dining area leads way to a set of French doors, opening to a private side yard w/ sitting area perfect for a quiet evening or entertaining family, friends, sipping a local Temecula Valley wine. Upstairs, the master suite boasts a gorgeous view of the Legends Golf Course, dual sinks in the master bath, walk-in shower, walk-in closet and a spacious jacuzzi tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day.  There are two additional bedrooms with full bathrooms as well as laundry room on the second floor.  Brand new HVAC unit, newer 200 amp electrical panel & 220 amp charging station in the garage for electric car hookups. **PAID SOLAR (40 panels) AND AUTO CHARGING STATION IN GARAGE** Fire SCE and the $7.00 a gallon gas charges. Garage is a tandem. Temeku HOA has too many features to list, Pools, spas, meeting rooms, trails, parks, dining rooms, work out gyms, GOLF etc....
